1. *Ućuti* je najbolje što možeš učiniti u ovoj situaciji. (It is best to remain silent in this situation.)
2. Ona nije mogla *ućutati*. (She couldn't keep quiet.)
3. On je *ućutao* kada je video tu sliku. (He remained silent when he saw that picture.)
4. Svi su *ućutali* kada je nastupio trenutak tišine. (Everyone was silent when the moment of silence came.)
5. Uvek je najbolje *ućutati* i čuti šta drugi imaju da kažu. (It is always best to remain silent and hear what other people have to say.)